   1:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c **** /*
   2:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c
   3:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * MSP: Microcontroller Support Package.
   4:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *
   5:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * La HAL separa la configuracion logica de un periferico (registros de modo,
   6:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * velocidad, formato) de su conexion fisica (reloj de bus, pines, NVIC).
   7:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * La primera vive en el modulo del periferico; la segunda se centraliza aqui,
   8:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * porque HAL_<PPP>_Init() invoca automaticamente a HAL_<PPP>_MspInit().
   9:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *
  10:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * Reunir toda la asignacion de pines en un unico archivo facilita detectar
  11:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * conflictos de recursos, que es el error mas comun al ampliar un proyecto.
  12:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *
  13:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  * Mapa de pines completo:
  14:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PA0  ADC1_IN0    VRX del joystick
  15:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PA1  ADC1_IN1    VRY del joystick
  16:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PA2  USART2_TX   consola serie (via ST-LINK)
  17:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PA3  USART2_RX   consola serie (via ST-LINK)
  18:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PA8  MCO1        salida de reloj conmutable
  19:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PB5  EXTI5       pulsador SW del joystick
  20:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PB8  I2C1_SCL    reloj del bus del LCD
  21:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PB9  I2C1_SDA    datos del bus del LCD
  22:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PH1  GPIO out    LED blinky
  23:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PC14 OSC32_IN    cristal LSE de 32.768 kHz
  24:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  *   PC15 OSC32_OUT   cristal LSE de 32.768 kHz
  25:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c ****  */
  26:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c **** #include "main.h"
  27:Core/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_msp.c **** 
